-- Reliance Industries Plans to Shut Crude Distillation Unit at Jamnagar
-- B y   P r a d e e p   K u r u p
-- 2010-10-22T09:46:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/reliance-industries-plans-to-shut-crude-distillation-unit-at-jamnagar.html
Reliance Industries Ltd. plans to
shut a crude distillation unit and a coker at its Jamnagar
refinery for maintenance for three to four weeks starting in the
last week of October, according to a statement on the Bombay
Stock Exchange today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Pradeep Kurup at 
 pkurup3@bloomberg.net  